source:
TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDBLUE_000_001<tab>But in the end, they are only that─savages.
Now, let us be brief. His Radiance awaits.
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDBLUE_000_001<tab>Но это дикари, так или иначе.
Покончим с этим. Его Великолепие ждёт.

source: TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDRED_000_010<tab>We have served our purpose. Come, we shall withdraw for now.
target: TEXT_DUNGEONBORDERAREA_00000_IMPERIALGUARDRED_000_010<tab>Мы исполнили свой приказ. А теперь — отходим!..
